---
title: Garlicky Mixed Mushroom Farro Bowl with Goat's Cheese and Candied Walnuts
description: Enjoy the warming woodland flavours of mixed mushrooms, garlic and toasty, chewy farro. An easy grain bowl that will quickly become a weeknight favourite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bol-de-farro-aux-champignons-et-a-lail-b039de27.jpg
